.TH "sfwbar-bsdctl" "1" "" ""
.SH Name
sfwbar-bsdctl \- Sfwbar BSD sysctl module
.sp
Filename: bsdctl.so
.sp
Requires: BSD libc
.SH SYNOPSIS
.sp
The BSDCtl module provides an interface to query BSD sysctl values
.SH Functions
.SS BSDCtl(Query)
.sp
Queries the value of a sysctl variable. It\(aqs equivalent to calling sysctl
